import React from "react";
import {
  Button,
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  Container,
  Col,
} from "reactstrap";

const LoginComponent = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Col md={6}>
        <Form>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label for="Username">Username</Label>
            <Input
              required
              type="text"
              name="text"
              id="textUser"
              placeholder="Masukkan Username..."
            />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label for="Password">Password</Label>
            <Input
              required
              type="password"
              name="password"
              id="textPassword"
              placeholder="Masukkan Password..."
            />
          </FormGroup>
          <Button>Submit</Button>
        </Form>
      </Col>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default LoginComponent;
